cd ~/Library/LaunchAgents launchctl unload com.sheepsystems.BookMacster.*.*.*.*.*.plist rm -f com.sheepsystems.BookMacster.*.*.*.*.*.plist # Asterisk 1 is: a UUID # Asterisk 2 is: the agent index # Asterisk 3 is: the trigger index # Asterisk 4 is: doSoon, doOver or standby # Asterisk 5 is: a PID, or noPid
